{\b 2. INTENDED USE OF GOOGLE ADS API\par}
\par
Primary Use Cases:\par
\par
1. Campaign Management\par
   - Create and manage Search, App, and Display campaigns\par
   - Update campaign budgets and bidding strategies\par
   - Pause/enable campaigns based on performance\par
\par
2. Ad Creation\par
   - Create responsive search ads with multiple headlines/descriptions\par
   - Create app install campaign assets\par
   - Update ad copy for A/B testing\par
\par
3. Reporting\par
   - Pull campaign performance metrics (impressions, clicks, conversions)\par
   - Generate daily/weekly performance reports\par
   - Monitor cost per install and cost per signup\par
\par
4. Keyword Management\par
   - Add/remove keywords from ad groups\par
   - Update keyword bids\par
   - Add negative keywords\par
\par

