{\b 4. TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION\par}
\par
Architecture:\par
- Backend: Node.js / TypeScript\par
- API Client: google-ads-api npm package\par
- Authentication: OAuth 2.0 with refresh tokens\par
- Hosting: Vercel / Firebase Functions\par
\par
API Operations Used:\par
- GoogleAdsService.Search - Reporting queries\par
- GoogleAdsService.Mutate - Create/update resources\par
- CampaignService - Campaign management\par
- AdGroupService - Ad group management\par
- AdGroupAdService - Ad creation\par
- KeywordService - Keyword management\par
\par
Estimated API Usage:\par
- Daily operations: Less than 1,000 (well under Basic limit of 15,000)\par
- Primary usage: Campaign creation, performance reporting\par
\par

{\b 5. DATA HANDLING\par}
\par
Data Storage:\par
- API credentials stored securely in environment variables\par
